**Project Proposal**

I would like to develop a project for Pawgrammers, a pet adoption shelter needs your help\! 

**Proposed Technical Stack**

* **MongoDB \+ Express \+ Node**: We will intend to use MongoDB for storage of data and authentication  
* **Vercel:** Frontend will be deployed on Vercel  
* **React:** The frontend will be all react. The app has been created using npx create-react-app to begin with.
